Ay-ṭfen ma fɣeɣ-d ɣef teqbaylit-iw.
yecbeḥ.
Ad y-ṭfen ma nnuɣeɣ ɣef tmaziɣt, yecbeḥ. 
Ɣef yizerfan n umdan, deg umaḍal.
Amennuɣ deg tmurt-iw, ɣef uɣref-iw yeffuden tilelli.
Ad y-ṭfen ma fɣeɣ-d ɣef tmeṭṭut, d lbaṭel yezgan fell-as.
Maca ad d-tefɣen ilmend n tmurt i tetten arraw-is, umi semman war isem-is.
Sentḍen-as tutlayt ur telli d tutlayt-is.
Ala d ta ur yecbiḥen ara, ad ak-ṭfen fell-as.
Limmer  meqqar amennuɣ yezdi tili tefra zik-nni. 
Amennuɣ yebḍa, iberdan mxalafen, timuɣliwin zegrent i wakkud-nsent, ala.
Ur d ay-ttaṭafen ara, imi ur d-ffiɣeɣ ara, akka kan. 
Bɣiɣ ad d-fɣeɣ maɛna ulac ɣer wanida, ulac d wanwa.
Akka kan!
Ur d-fiɣeɣ ara.
Sureft-iyi ur d-fiɣeɣ ara.
Tarwan leḥlal inejren abrid i tlelli. 
Rran-asen takmamt, nnan-asen zemmet imi. 
Siwel neɣ qim, ulac win ara d-yeslen. 
Ayɣer ad ak-d-slen atnin ceṭḥen. 
I tmeṭṭut i rran lekben nnan-as kemm d taɛkumt. 
Limmer kan ǧǧan-t ad texdem, nettat tezmer i umdegger. 
Anda tebɣiḍ attan tezwar. 
D iḥerqan neɣ d icerfan, ula d tayri-s d imennuɣen. 
Rfed neɣ sers. 
Awi neɣ eǧǧ. 
Qbel neɣ agi. 
Bɣu neɣ qim. 
Iff xir ad as-terreḍ leḥsan. 
D ta i d tameṭṭut ad ak-imlen tudert. 
Lḥif d kra yuɛren. 
Yid-s ad twaliḍ tafat i d-yufraren, seg sirem i tettrebbi s ɣur-s. 
Aḥeq kra yekkan gar-aneɣ. 
D wayen akk yezgan yid-neɣ. 
Tecrek-aɣ tagella d lemleḥ. 

